Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.13,0:00:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.26,0:00:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
