Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,角斗赛要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the joust
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.31,0:01:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟着你呢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right behind you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,574)}中世纪时刻
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到中世纪时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Medieval Moments
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们只需再走上二十巫师步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just 20 wizard's paces away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即可体验剑术巫术  及恶劣卫生条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from swords, sorcery and bad hygiene
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, please
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  兄台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, my good man
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.13,0:01:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吾认为汝应说  此处请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe thou meant to say, "Righteth this wayeth"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someday
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,羊肉好不好吃  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that mutton, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看羊肉味道好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me thinks it's mutton-tastic
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莫里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morrie
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.32,0:01:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要宣布角斗赛开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to announce the jousting tournament
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.53,0:02:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  各位中世纪时刻的观众们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, uh, fair patrons of Medieval Moments
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.89,0:02:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依照皇家法令  我们将要求两名观众
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By royal decree, we ask that two audience members
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来上台参加那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come forth and participate in the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇家角斗赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the royal jousting
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快选  选我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick up, pick us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.07,0:02:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.61,0:02:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.47,0:02:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来粉海星跟黄海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the pink starfish and the yellow sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我们今晚的幸运参与者了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are our lucky contestants tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激不激动啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exciting, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然马上就能近距离观赏角斗赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To think, we'll be watching the joust this close up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不是来观赏角斗赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be watching the joust
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是来参加角斗赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in the joust
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你会骑海马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, do you know how to ride a sea horse?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海马先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sea Horse, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会不会对新手温柔点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're gentle on beginners, aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, help
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,取他首级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take his head off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在好像不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose now would be a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请求上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ask for a bathroom break
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐厅的员工过来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some employees from the restaurant came to help us
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮捕这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrest these traitors
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.86,0:03:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罪名是从天而降施法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for committing the act of witchcraft
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by falling from the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整得真是比真实还真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They really go that extra mile for authenticity
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向骑士同伴们致意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salutations, fellow knights
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要吵  异端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence, heathen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get the point
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nighty-night, ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老老实实坐牢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have many more in here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这些道具好逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Pat, these props sure are convincing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么破烂乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blast this confounded instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我一直都吹不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I never learn to play with ease
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may mine own
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾曾曾曾曾曾曾孙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,great, great, great, great, great, great, great grandson
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受十倍诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be cursed tenfold
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝同吾言乎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does thou talketh to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.02,0:04:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝同吾言乎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Does thou talketh to me?"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勿哂之  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scoff not, young squire
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝认错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thou has mistaken me for another
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.66,0:04:43.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我乃章鱼兄  国王之弄臣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:43.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Squidly, the king's royal fool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我被贬入狱之前还是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or at least I was until I royally messed up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么被贬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尝为国王心爱的弄臣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was the king's favorite fool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将欢笑带到世间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made merry mirth and laughter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲了个冷笑话  国王中风倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I told one bad joke and the king had a stroke
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是我被挂于房椽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I hang from ye ol' rafter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得在这干什么才能有羊肉吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does a guy have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get some mutton around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可饿死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得真是美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't hold thy breath
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二世纪咱还能有东西吃就算走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be lucky if we get fed again by the 12th century
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边人表演得还挺认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They sure take their role-playing seriously around here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶巫师之龙来临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The evil wizard's dragon is here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四方百姓惊声尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See the townsfolk scream with fear
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四方百姓慌忙奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See the townsfolk try to run
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切显然不欢不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can tell this won't be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶龙欲要焚烧一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dragon will torch everything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山谷万物尽数消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything in the valley
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医院学校与养老院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hospitals, schools, retirement homes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,562)}养老院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,572)}保龄球馆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连保龄球馆也不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And even Ye Olde Bowling Alley
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰保龄球馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the bowling alley
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骑士  弄臣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knights, jesters
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶龙  中世纪保龄球馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dragons, medieval bowling alleys
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,12th century
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不明白吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you see, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们真的穿越到中世纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We really are in medieval times
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家水龙头好像忘关了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I left the water running at home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王要跟你们两个说个话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The king wants a word with you two
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要走就要带章鱼兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't leave without Squidly
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么要带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why should I take him?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because, um
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼兄给国王想了些好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidly has thought of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some brilliant songs for the king
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须得让国王听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he just has to hear them
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对  章鱼兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Squidly?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidly, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是见着国王再吹好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe you should wait for the king to hear that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suit thine self
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝不知艺之失也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thou does not knowest what thou art missing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woe is me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woe is me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What to do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.81,0:06:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,父王  汝缘何而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Father, what art thou going on about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是同样那件事  亲爱的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just the same old thing, dear daughter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个可恨的痞老巫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that wretched wizard, Planktonimor
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他阴险狡诈的恶龙毁了我大半个王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His insidious dragons destroyed half me kingdom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将来就不会有国民来交税了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon there will be no citizens to tax
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好的骑士们就没一个能打败他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not one of me best knights has been able to defeat him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,父王  别忘了您的高血压
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Father, remember your blood pressure
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您应该不想再来一次水蛭疗法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want another leech treatment, would you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Highness
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地下城主把您要召见的囚犯带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dungeon Master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has brought the prisoners you asked for
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就不要傻站着  带他们进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't just stand there, send them in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Your Highness
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胆敢以那样的语气叫我  混账
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you bark at me in that tone, knave?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是这个王国最受敬畏的统治者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the feared ruler of this kingdom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对我讲话要尊重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and will be addressed as such
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你们为什么把这弄臣带回我正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why have you brought this fool
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back into me throne room?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请陛下大发慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If your majesty may be so kind
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有首歌可以回答您所有的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I have a song
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will answer all your questions
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好那好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这回是你最后的机会  弄臣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is your last chance, fool
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sire, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会让您失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be disappointed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王请您听我唱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, hear me, King, for I must sing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尔可谓样样精通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How you are the greatest at everything
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放纵恶龙烧全城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like letting a dragon burn down our city
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美景已然不再成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A horrible sight that wasn't pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝之过错皆可憎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Twas all your fault and 'tis a pity
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尔甚恶难辞其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were bad, you are to blame
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绞汝尊首以耻之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now hang your kingly head in shame
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王甚恶难辞其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The king is bad, the king's to blame
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绞其尊首以耻之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He hangs his kingly head in shame
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这些造谣诽谤的送上断头台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send these slanderers to the guillotine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not from here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们是巫师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because you're witches
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奉痞老巫的命要来灭掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who were sent by Planktonimor to destroy me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是穿越来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're time travelers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me out here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不清楚有没有什么话可以帮你找补
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure there's anything I can add at this point
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够这些儿戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm through playing around
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,父王  您必须要饶了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Father, you must spare them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝仍记预言否
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has thou forgotten of the prophecy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.66,0:09:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么预言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What prophecy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在您头顶正上方的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one right above your head
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意在上面多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long has that been there?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预言说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The story tells
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有两个从天而降的勇敢骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of two brave knights who fall from the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会被国王派遣  让可怜的小镇摆脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and are sent by the king to rid the lamenting town
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.40,0:09:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受控于独眼巫师的恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the evil dragon controlled by the one-eyed wizard
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,父王  您就不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Father, don't you get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些陌生人过来拯救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These strangers have come to rescue us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟预言讲的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like in the prophecy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胆敢玷污我的王宫  恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you defile my house, demon?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Princess Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好受死吧  禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to meet thy maker, foul beast
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都要结束了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I-I guess this is it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想你的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也会想你的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you, too, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,父王  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy, help
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就没人能阻止这乱局的蔓延吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can no one stop this madness?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.97,0:10:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接受我的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My apologies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最崇高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,most noble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最尊敬的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and valued
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,warriors
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的皇家礼遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this is what you call the royal treatment
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿海神保佑你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May Neptune grant you safety
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.35,0:10:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,披荆斩棘  平安抵达邪恶巫师城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on your perilous journey to the evil wizard's castle
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那里从来没有人能活着逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from which no one has escaped alive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,路上有很多艰难险阻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going on a perilous journey?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But of course
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可是救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the chosen ones
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,失踪的一块预言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A lost piece of the prophecy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是赞扬我们英雄气概的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more praise for our heroic stature?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  上面画着我应该把你们踢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it says I was supposed to kick you out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多说了  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say no more, Your Majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们英勇骑士特别英勇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Us manly knights are so manly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自个踢自个出去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we kick ourselves out of places
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.82,0:11:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心了  大恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用他们陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, so much for their company
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我思索再三  你得跟他们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On second thought, you better go with them
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可以拿你寻欢作乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They could use the entertainment
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have it your way
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck, strange ones
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我们确实被预言选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know we're a prophecy and all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.98,0:11:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是手无寸铁应该没法阻止恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can stop the dragon with our bare hands
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说得整点铁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need some gloves
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能那边的铁匠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps yonder blacksmith
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给你们作战提供装备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could provide some arms for your battle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,368)}铁匠
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有位辛勤的劳动者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An honest man of the soil
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我轻松跟这野蛮本地人打成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Observe as I effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,commingle with this brutish native
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  铁匠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Iron Man
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝爵士  来自裤头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Sir SpongeBob, of Bikini
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老早就告诉过你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you people before
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有钱自然会交租
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have the rent when I have it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是要来买武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to buy some armor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just say that?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好有适合你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got just the thing for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is awesome
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  出来下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, get out here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你看起来可真是妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you look incredible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在奉上防卫武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, for the piece de resistance
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的剑  勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your sword, brave knight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以阳极电镀龙皮为材料亲手锻造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand-forged from anodized dragon's skin
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这武器绝对可以配上你们这样的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is truly a weapon worthy of a knight of your stature
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little heavy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这伤得要缝好几针了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's going to need some stitches
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找下还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see what else I got
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常不幸  我手上的轻型武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, all I have in the way of light weaponry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这把水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is this jellyfish net
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还有很长的路得走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We doth have a long journey ahead of us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我给咱打包了干粮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I packed us a lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是美味的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of delicious krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,传说中的预言就这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This be the legendary prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1006,830)}电话簿
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That be-eth rich
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直是在侮辱我  这样就不好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,T'would almost insult me, were it not so funny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.40,0:13:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老巫  汝属实过分自大矣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Planktonimor, thou art cocky
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and overly-confident with thyself
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我吧  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trusteth in me, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doth knowest what I am doing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这来  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come hither, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.95,0:13:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我的战书下放给蟹国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deliver my demands unto his majesty, King Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.31,0:14:12.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:12.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.93,0:14:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没看错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doth mine eyes betray me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是邪恶的黑暗骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Tis the nefarious Dark Knight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑暗骑士  我来求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dark Knight, spare us please
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别砍掉头  膝盖莫搞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cut off our heads or boil our knees
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带离他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pray, take these two
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我远走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And let me go free
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会给你送来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I will give to thee some
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑暗骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dark Knight?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再问一个问题  然后就肢解你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I asketh once more, before I rip thee limb from limb
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reveal thyself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝  这位是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am SpongeBob, and this is Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是派来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been spent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从痞老巫手里救出珍珍公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to rescue Princess Pearl from Planktonimor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝欲过此路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If thou wisheth to get across
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须过我这关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thou willst have to get through me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中世纪珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Medieval Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么个对付法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to handle this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整点空手道就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a little karate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the hammer of Odin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这居然是我从来没见过的全新招式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this be a new fighting style mine eyes have not yet seen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am bad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝欲辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doth thou tryeth to insult me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必先自取其辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thou whilst drink from the fountain of shame
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说她会松鼠似的突过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you she zings like a squir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厉害  中世纪珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, medieval Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你能对付得了我的怒火之脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But can you handle my feet of fury?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想来摩擦摩擦一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldst thou like a little rubdown?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打败我了  黄骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have bested me, yellow knight
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打得真是快准狠  勇士海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strike quick and true, noble sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂你刚刚说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a word you just said
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中世纪珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Medieval Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的样子不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't look so good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.90,0:16:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你饶了我一命  好心的勇士海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thou hast spared me, kind and noble sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为对你们的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and to thee, I owe a debt of gratitude
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我将跟随你们一同踏上征程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for I will follow you in your quest
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打败痞老巫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to defeat Planktonimor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.87,0:16:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便跟你学空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and learn a trifle of that karate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陛下  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your majesty, your majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有份卷轴要寄给您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A scroll hath arrived for thee
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汝须交出城池
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Thou must hand over thy village
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,及宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and thy throne?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则汝之女将坠入岩浆大釜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or thy daughter shall be dipped in a cauldron of lava?"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是公主的惨叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That be the shriek of the fair princess
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.14,0:17:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倾听公主  塔上惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hark, the princess, she screams from the tower
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.86,0:17:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼声表明  其命难保
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the sound of her shrieks, this is her final hour
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧要关头到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then time be of the essence
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doth we all remember thy plan?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.16,0:17:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I said
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let us forge on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way, heathens
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑暗骑士要过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dark Knight coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请表明你的来意  黑暗骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,State thy business, Dark Knight
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些土包子图谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These village idiots are conspirators
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要对痞老巫大人造反
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,against Master Planktonimor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要知道痞老巫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I needeth to know which form of torture
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想怎么折磨这些可怜的蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thy master wishes upon these wretched fools
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.30,0:18:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以五马分尸他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I have their limbs tied to horses
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and swiftly yanked apart--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是一根一根拔掉眼睫毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or pluck each individual eyelash, one by one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.83,0:18:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们连愿望都许不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,taking away their every single last eyelash wish?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  黑暗骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very well, Dark Knight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准许进入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Entrance be granted
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拔根睫毛许个愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make a wish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这办法真不错  海绵宝宝爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodsome thinking, Sir SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现得跟个穿尿布的小屁孩似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,posing as a frightened wee babe in ye old diapers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们想不信都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,did make it most believable
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得我们骗到他们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you think we fooled them?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Princess Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须得让预言成真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must fulfill the prophecy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你去给派大星跟那个卖傻的松绑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while you untie Patrick and the royal doofus
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫弄臣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That be royal fool
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're coming to rescue you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freedom is at hand
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're a-coming
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王的城池马上就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon, the king's village will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unhand her
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fiend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预言就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The prophecy is nigh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是来救你的  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to rescue you, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能来杯水喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,666)}苏打水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要苏打水还是纯净水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sparkling or regular?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(614,814)}纯净水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Psyche-eth
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你整个就是裤头郡最讨人嫌的巫师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You truly are the nastiest wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in all of Bikini Bottomshire
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好战败吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be vanquished
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来吧  混账
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on-eth, knave
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.22,0:19:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没看到你  你小死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you, you're so tiny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法力真小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tiny powers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I be-eth okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快电他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sicceth them, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能来首柔和短歌可以让你静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a soothing limerick will calm thee
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有条龙  英俊又聪慧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There once was a dragon so handsome and smart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.77,0:20:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它心胸宽广  让我自由而归
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He let me go free, for he had a big heart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都好会批评
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone be-eth a critic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们已经是死路一条了  小白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dead end for you, simpletons
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来的人肯定不会相信这回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boys back home will never believe this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是在这都不信这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, and I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大限还是到了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is it, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在咱可以吃蟹黄堡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we eat those krabby patties now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它在吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's eating the krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horror, the horror
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.00,0:21:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是大好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's a good thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure it is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听它呼噜叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just listen to him purr
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.55,0:21:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可太爱吃蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He loves that krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.69,0:21:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底是在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forsooth, what be-eth going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Destroy them
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我马上就灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it now, or so help me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会很乐意再给你做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd be more than happy to make you some more
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃的蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of those delicious krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curses
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.28,0:22:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.18,0:22:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都让条道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王的英雄们要过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thy king's heroes cometh through
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听钟声响起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hark, ring the bell
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皆大欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Tis all ended well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.25,0:22:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶龙已被征服  公主完成归途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dragon is vanquished, the princess returned
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.21,0:22:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们中只有一两个被烧得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And only a few of us got badly burned
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道可不可以卖这些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doth wonder if I couldst sell these
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难听死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That horrible noise
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他别吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们刚摔得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was some fall you had
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.46,0:23:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真不该激怒那只海马
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't have agitated that sea horse
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.73,0:23:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚的梦还精彩吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was some dream, huh, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.90,0:23:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这话还是跟章鱼兄讲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try telling that to Squidly
